            <h3>Printing and Copying in Kouvola Libraries</h3>
            
            <p>All Kouvola libraries offer printing services that enable, for example, remote printing from your home computer and releasing print jobs at any Kouvola library.</p>
            <p><b>Register</b> before your first library print, copy, or scan by swiping your library card at the printer’s card reader and entering your card PIN.</p>
            <p><b>Printing and copying</b> are fee-based. Check the prices on the <a href="https://kyyti.finna.fi/Content/maksut-kouvola" target="_blank">Kouvola fees page</a>. You can print from a library computer or your own device. 
